  "author": "",
  "description": "## Summary\nThis extension is useful if you want to trigger only once per instance.\nThis is simpler than creating your own instance variables.\n\n## How to use: \n- Adding the **Only Once Condition** behavior to an object.\n- In the events add the **Only Once** condition to the instance.\n\nThe condition will be identified by the **condition name** and will be executed only once until you reset if you want using it one more time.\n\nThis extension add:\n\n- **Only Once Condition** - behavior\n- **Only Once** - condition\n- **Reset all conditions** - action\n- **Reset condition** - action",
